        <applicationDomain>C4ISR &amp; C2 platform</applicationDomain>
        <description>The Link16 FOM v1.0 Draft 2 has been adapted for the Maritime Theatre Missile Defense (MTMD) SITE simulation environment (called 'SITE Federation'):
- order: timestamp instead of receive
- timestamps/lookahead: HLAfloat64Time instead of VerifierIntegerTime 
- removed basic types: Unsignedinteger64BE, UnsignedInteger16BE, UnsignedInteger32BE
- added simple types: Integer64, UnsignedInteger32, UnsignedInteger16
- added fixed record type: RTTABStruct
- renamed octetArray1, octetArray2 to OctetArray1, OctetArray2
- OctetArray1, OctetArray2 encodings: HLAfixedArray instead of Undefined
- renamed TADILJWordStructArray2 to TADILJWordStructArray
- TADILJWordStructArray encoding: HLAvariableArray instead of Undefined
- TADILJWordStructArray cardinality: Dynamic instead of [1..2147483647]
- Link16RadioSignal parameters: HLAbyte instead of HLAoctet, Integer64 instead of LongLong1, UnsignedInteger32 instead of UnsignedLong1, UnsignedInteger16 instead of UnsignedShort1
- JTIDSTransmitterStruct fields: UnsignedInteger32 instead of UnsignedLong1
- JTIDSVoiceCVSDRadioSignal, JTIDSVoiceLPC10RadioSignal, JTIDSVoiceLPC12RadioSignal parameters: HLAopaqueData instead of octetArray3
- removed synchronization points: First, Second
- removed all notes</description>
