                                <name>TSEC_CVLL</name>
                                <dataType>HLAbyte</dataType>
                                <semantics>Transmission Security, an integer identification of the crypto variable used for JTIDS transmission encryption. This variable allows for simulated crypto netting. A value of 255 shall indicate a no statement/wildcard.</semantics>
                            </parameter>
                            <parameter>
                                <name>MSEC_CVLL</name>
                                <dataType>HLAbyte</dataType>
                                <semantics>Message Security, an integer identification of the crypto variable used to encode the JTIDS message. This variable allows for simulated crypto netting. A value of 255 shall indicate a no statement/wildcard.</semantics>
